@metroid then you're not as wise as you think you are. For this to be NTR she has to be introduced as having a significant other or partner in a BST relationship, and then be shown having an intimate relationship with another man.

Her introduction was less having a husband than it was her simply being a housewife. Her partner hasn't once appeared and is highly inconsequential in this story. Thus, he can't evoke feelings of jealousy, as the SO should in a regular NTR story. Also, their first encounter was far from intimate; that was full-on rape.

Furthermore, as the son plays no part in Yuko's romantic life, this is just between her and Marquis. The story then becomes a simple rape cum cheating one.
